---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About • Peiyuan Ma"
  description="Who I am, what I'm learning, and what I'm building."
>
  <h1>About</h1>

  <section>
    <h2>Quick intro</h2>
    <p>
      I’m Peiyuan (Bobby) Ma — a cybersecurity student building a practical portfolio through
      projects, lab exercises, and writing. This site is where I ship work, document
      results, and track progress as I level up.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>What I’m aiming for</h2>
    <p>
      I’m interested in defensive security: how systems fail, how attacks show up in
      telemetry, and how to design controls that are realistic to operate.
    </p>
    <p>
      I’m also building up my fundamentals (networking, Linux, scripting) so I can
      go from “I understand the idea” to “I can implement and validate it.”
    </p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Home lab</h2>
    <p>
      I run a small Ubuntu server as a learning platform — monitoring, alerts, and
      automation included. Over time, I’ll publish writeups on what I build and the
      problems I hit along the way (deployments, hardening, and debugging included).
    </p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Tools I’m using</h2>
    <div class="tool-grid">
      <div class="tool-category">
        <h3>Foundations</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Networking basics (routing, DNS, HTTP)</li>
          <li>Linux administration</li>
          <li>Shell scripting</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="tool-category">
        <h3>Security learning</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Log investigation mindset</li>
          <li>Threat modeling basics</li>
          <li>Web security fundamentals</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="tool-category">
        <h3>Build & deploy</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Astro (this site)</li>
          <li>Git / GitHub</li>
          <li>Cloudflare Tunnel (CGNAT-friendly)</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="tool-category">
        <h3>Next up</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Docker + reverse proxy routing</li>
          <li>More structured labs + writeups</li>
          <li>Security automation projects</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>
      Best way to reach me: <a href="mailto:mpy.peiyuan@gmail.com">mpy.peiyuan@gmail.com</a>.
      You can also find me on <a href="https://github.com/bmstylish" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub</a>
      and <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/mpy-bobby" target="_blank" rel="noopener">LinkedIn</a>.
    </p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  section {
    margin-bottom: calc(var(--spacing-unit) * 6);
  }

  .tool-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
    gap: calc(var(--spacing-unit) * 4);
    margin-top: calc(var(--spacing-unit) * 3);
  }

  .tool-category h3 {
    font-size: 1rem;
    margin-top: 0;
    margin-bottom: calc(var(--spacing-unit) * 2);
    color: var(--color-text-heading);
  }

  .tool-category ul {
    list-style: none;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .tool-category li {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    margin-bottom: calc(var(--spacing-unit) * 1);
    padding-left: calc(var(--spacing-unit) * 2);
    position: relative;
  }

  .tool-category li::before {
    content: '›';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--color-accent);
  }
</style>
